{"author":"Sunan Abu Dawud","hadith":{"hadithnumber":3979,"arabicnumber":3979,"text":"। আবূ সাঈদ (রাঃ) সূত্রে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম এভাবে পড়তেনঃ (مِنْ ضُعْفٍ)।[1] হাসান।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":32,"hadith":11}}}